Package: epoxy
Title: String Interpolation for 'R Markdown' Documents
Version: 0.0.2.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Garrick", "Aden-Buie", , "garrick@adenbuie.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7111-0077"))
Description: Extra strength 'glue' for data-driven templating. String
    interpolation for 'R Markdown' documents and 'Shiny' apps, built on
    the 'glue' and 'whisker' packages.
